title: Freeman runs for 116 yards as Falcons edge Titans 10-7
text:
> Georgia Freeman runs for 116 yards as Falcons edge Titans 10-7 Atlanta Falcons free safety Robenson Therezie (27) runs back a pass interception to stop the final drive of the Tennessee Titans as quarterback Matt Ryan (2) celebrates on the sideline in the final minutes of the fourth quarter of an NFL football game Sunday, Oct. 25, 2015, in Nashville, Tenn. Atlanta won 10-7. (AP Photo/Weston Kenney) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
